---
description: PageGrid — carousels align to column 7; screen strip matches PackUp
---

- **Column 7:** On `PageGrid` (`grid-cols-8`), when main copy sits in `md:col-start-3 md:col-span-4` (columns 3–6), wrap horizontal carousels and full-bleed strips in `extendContentToCol7Class` from `src/lib/sectionLayout.ts` so the scroller reaches column 7.
- **Dedicated screens row:** Prefer `md:col-start-3 md:col-span-5` for a bottom “Screens” carousel (columns 3–7), not `col-span-6`.
- **Screen carousel strip (like PackUp):** Inner row `flex gap-6 md:gap-14 w-max pr-[20%]`; each screen image `h-[240px] md:h-[380px] w-auto rounded-sm pointer-events-none`.
